ud of its kind the gang fooled  bidders who they arrogantly described as idiots into paying for goods that did not exist victims from around the world handed over sums of up to pounds  for everything from concert tickets to motorbikes through the money transfer chain western union   david brown december   fraudsters targeted in new ebay crackdown the people p  the auction giant will protect customers by banning the use of online money transfers now ebay will bring in the ban – backed by western union and already in force in the us – from january  in the uk it will tell punters to use secure payment systems that verify the identity of users and which can track both buyers and sellers accounts   trust  safety blog  western union and trade me members a terrible combination retrieved  may    a b western union admits to aiding wire fraud to pay  mln   central bank fines western union €m the irish times  may    settlement agreement between the central bank and western union payment services ireland limited central bank of ireland  may    suskind ron  the one percent doctrine deep inside americas pursuit of its enemies since  simon  schuster isbn    ming the mechanic western union sucks – the newslog of flemming funch  sundaram anjan july   muslims denied wire transfers – business – international herald tribune the new york times retrieved november     a b c d lost in intermediation pdf overseas development institute   wwwdwcom deutsche welle opinion migrant money transfers or development aid  africa  dw   dwcom retrieved    sending money home contributing to the sdgs one family at a time international fund for agricultural development ifad   moré iñigo fighting exclusivity clauses in the market for remittances pdf remesasorg   western union quizzed by eu on money transfer activities euractivcom retrieved   further readingedit wolff joshua d western union and the creation of the american corporate order – new york cambridge university press  external linksedit wikimedia co